description:
WellChair
786 unique nfts have been made available to the community.
WellChair; It can be integrated into future metaverse projects as a unique nft and can be actively used in these metaverses.
WellChair was established to address people who use wheelchairs to always emerge victorious from the challenges they face by creating social awareness in the metaverse universe.
In the metaverse universes, people using our community nfts will move faster and become more advantageous. In this way, people who use wheelchairs will be aware that they can overcome everything and should not feel any difference.
Nft owners will be regularly airdropped every month and a 3d printed figure of their nft will be given as a gift.

After the collection is created, 20% of the revenues and 20% of the gas fee revenues will be donated to wheelchair needs, through global or local charities, as power chairs. All remaining revenue will be used for marketing and project development.
name: Well Chair
